description: Apply this rule when drafting or revising SADS design spec rows so requirements follow EARS, stay atomic, and describe concrete deterministic workflows.
globs:
  - "**/design_spec*.csv"
  - "**/*SADS*.csv"
  - "docs/csv_contracts.md"
alwaysApply: false
